metadata.changes: Change 1: Replace sentence += f"{triple.subject} {triple.predicate} {triple.object}. " with 9 lines

diff_user.system:
You are an expert in fixing your collegues code. You know that the code should be in format:
<<<<<<< SEARCH
# Original code to find and replace (must match exactly, indentations and endlines as well)
=======
# New replacement code
>>>>>>> REPLACE
Provided the incorrect format of SEARCH/REPLACE fix it to a correct format.
diff_user.user:
An incorrect diff format was detected in this change:
```diff
<<<<<<< HEAD
    sentence += f"{triple.subject} {triple.predicate} {triple.object}. "
=======
    if i > 0 and triples[i-1].subject == triple.subject:
        sentence += f", {triple.predicate} {triple.object}. "
    else:
        if triple.predicate == "country" and i > 0:
            sentence += f" and is located in {triple.object}. "
        elif triple.predicate == "capital" and i > 0:
            sentence += f", which has {triple.object} as its capital. "
        else:
            sentence += f"{triple.subject} {triple.predicate} {triple.object}. "
>>>>>>> REPLACE
```
Please fix it to the correct format.
